// Note:
//   You must download the VGG-19 model before using 'art_style.py'!
//   (The pretrained model is too big(~510) to upload to github)
//   Please refer to 
//     ./artistic/pretrained-model/imagenet-vgg-verydeep-19.mat.download_address
//

Usage:
>> python3 art_style.py -c CONTENT -s STYLE 
                        [--num_iter [NUM_ITER]] [-i [INIT]]
Example:
>> python3 art_style.py -c tiananmen.jpg -s starry.jpg --num_iter=100 (defaut 300)

Generated images would be written to the ./output folder,
At the end, learning curves would also be plotted.

//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Neruo Style Transfer.

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -c CONTENT, --content CONTENT
                        the style image
  -s STYLE, --style STYLE
                        the style image
  -i [INIT], --init [INIT]
                        the initial image
  --num_iter [NUM_ITER]
                        the initial image
                        